            <h1>Gameplay</h1>
        <p>
           Based on the style of the previous parts, but instead of planting on a yard, you may switch to other yard(s) and defend 
           your lawns. The zombies on the main screen and sub screen(s) will still approach your house even you switch the yard
           so keep your brains safe.
        </p>
